## Key Technical Concepts
### Load Balancing Layers
- **Layer 4**: TCP/UDP level, faster (~1ms), no content inspection, session persistence challenges
- **Layer 7**: Application level, intelligent routing, SSL termination, content-based rules (~5ms overhead)

### Algorithms Comparison
